snippet.title: Elium - Prison Escape // Teaser
snippet.description:
Teaser trailer for Elium - Prison Escape 
http://www.eliumgame.com

Take the role of Jarren Sorengar, a former master swordsman seeing his days pass as a war weary prisoner. Time has come to meet fate, find an escape or die in the attempt. 

For news and details about Elium - Prison Escape, follow on social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EliumGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/EliumGame
